UNOSAT is now recognized as the United Nations Satellite Centre 📡 #PhotoOfTheWeek

@unitar.unosat uses satellite imaging and geospatial observation to support humanitarian relief in fields such as refugee protection, human rights, natural disasters, cultural heritage and climate change.

Hosting UNOSAT allows us to use our technology to benefit society: not only do we help the UNOSAT teams to store their data and download geospatial information rapidly, but we also develop new projects together like #artificialintelligence algorithms to enhance UNOSAT analysis.
